    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/morningside" style="color:#c4912a;">Morningside</a>, <a href="/suburbs/carina" style="color:#c4912a;">Carina</a>, <a href="/suburbs/murarrie" style="color:#c4912a;">Murarrie</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

