        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Cannon Hill sits within easy reach of Morningside, Hawthorne and the Gateway Motorway, making it practical for families and professionals alike. The suburb has a quiet, established character and good local primary schools that resonate with family buyers upsizing from inner-city apartments.</p>
